 **Analytics & Testing**

* **Vendor Management & Third-Party Integrations:** Manage relationships with third-party service providers, including appraisal management companies (AMC), title companies, and credit reporting agencies, ensuring smooth integration into the origination workflow.


* **Business Process Documentation:** Create and maintain comprehensive process documentation, including **SOPs (Standard Operating Procedures)**, user manuals, system configuration guides, and training materials for end-users.


* **System Testing & User Acceptance Testing (UAT):** Lead system testing efforts for new LOS features, enhancements, and third-party integrations. Ensure the accuracy and performance of the system by conducting **User Acceptance Testing (UAT)** with stakeholders and ensuring sign-off before deployment.


* **Regulatory Updates & Change Management:** Keep the organization updated on **mortgage regulation changes**, ensure timely implementation of necessary system updates, and manage change control processes for new features or compliance mandates.
